Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.71,0:01:12.71,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,在缓缓流淌的河上喝冷饮最爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:12.71,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing beats a cool drink on a lazy river
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.71,0:01:13.51,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:13.51,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,eh, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.88,0:01:15.93,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:15.93,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said it, pal!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.60,0:01:25.48,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:25.48,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Waterfall!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.70,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,手套乐园感谢你们游玩挫伤瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.70,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glove World thanks you for riding Contusion Falls.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.78,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎康复后再来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.78,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come again, after you've healed.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.28,0:01:42.24,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:42.24,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We will!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.24,0:01:43.62,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能没等康复就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:43.62,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could be sooner!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.84,0:01:54.84,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:54.84,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.09,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天最棒的时间要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.09,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the best time of the day!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.89,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,烧烤时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.89,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barbecue time?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.89,0:01:59.72,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:01:59.72,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的是做剪贴簿的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about scrapbooking!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.22,0:02:06.39,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要把今天的记忆保存一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:06.39,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna save the memory of today forever!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.44,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.44,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forever!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.44,0:02:08.48,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:08.48,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.15,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.15,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.49,0:02:15.99,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:15.99,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.70,0:02:21.70,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:21.70,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.87,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,往日时光  美好往日时光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.87,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,The old days, good old days...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.04,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.04,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.04,0:02:28.29,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就该放《经典》这本里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:28.29,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You belong with the classics!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.04,0:02:30.75,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:30.75,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.75,0:02:34.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我能永远记住今天的点点滴滴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:34.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'll always remember today exactly as it happened!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.51,0:02:36.84,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,回首往事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:36.84,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Memory lane!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.26,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都很想要想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.26,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to remember
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得起事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,to remember things!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.60,0:02:43.60,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:43.60,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember this?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.72,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会飞的那会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.72,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I could fly?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.06,0:02:45.72,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:45.72,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.06,0:02:46.72,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:46.72,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.64,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.64,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.23,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在泡泡碗演出的那会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.23,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,When we performed at the Bubble Bowl?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.31,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.31,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.07,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你一定记得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.07,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll definitely remember...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.53,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我撕破我自己裤子的那会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.53,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I ripped my pants!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.15,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定自己真记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.15,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure you remember it?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.82,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那张好像是我爸撕破你裤子才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.82,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause that looks like my dad ripped your pants!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.32,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.32,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.12,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我记得自己有撕破过我裤子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.12,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I definitely remember ripping my pants.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.12,0:03:08.45,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,但不记得自己变过你爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:08.45,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I don't remember being your dad.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.66,0:03:10.96,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有你妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:10.96,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or your mom.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.63,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有你爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.63,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or your grandpa!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.29,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.29,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.34,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些人我一个都不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.34,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't remember any of those people!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.17,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.17,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.51,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道那是什么意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.51,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know what that means?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.14,0:03:23.47,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:23.47,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do not.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.47,0:03:26.01,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思就是出现了大坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:26.01,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It means something terrible is going on!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.73,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须马上就去你爸妈家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.73,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to get to your parents' house right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:29.85,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}《珍藏回忆》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.44,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}高菲高伯
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.24,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.24,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gar{\fn微软雅黑\fs50}ç{\fn方正兰亭中黑_GBK\fs40}on!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.70,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一桌双球圣代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.70,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another round of double-scoop sundaes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.12,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.12,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,s'il vous pla{\fn微软雅黑\fs50}î{\fn方正兰亭中黑_GBK\fs40}t!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.70,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个就不能滚别的地方去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.70,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you two have somewhere else to be?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.33,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.33,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.33,0:03:51.37,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:51.37,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.37,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那圣代就打包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.37,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better make those sundaes to go!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.35,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,海星爸妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.35,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. And Mrs. Star?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.02,0:04:11.98,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,是厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:11.98,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,The kitchen!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.81,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈肯定在下厨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.81,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom must be cooking!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.61,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.61,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.78,0:04:21.86,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:21.86,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.86,0:04:25.16,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈一定在做她的招牌垃圾砂锅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:25.16,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom must be making her famous trasherole!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.99,0:04:32.00,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤面包机发疯了  好像还饿着肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:32.00,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,The toaster's gone feral and it seems hungry.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.00,0:04:32.58,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:32.58,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.29,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,给它喂你钱包吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.29,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's feed it your wallet!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.39,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你反应可真快  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.39,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick thinking, Patrick.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.52,0:04:55.27,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我突然反应出来  家人就在楼上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:55.27,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm quick thinking that my family's upstairs.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.77,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.77,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.98,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爸跟派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.98,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Between my dad and GrandPat
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.53,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,总有一个会在上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.53,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,someone's always in the bathroom!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.69,0:05:04.82,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:04.82,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.28,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.28,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyone in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.41,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.41,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be Dad.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.20,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大爷从来不冲水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.20,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,GrandPat never flushes.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.09,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿尿也发疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.09,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tinkle's gone feral too.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.92,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下有点乱套了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.92,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a bit of a mess.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.67,0:05:23.80,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:23.80,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.92,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.92,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,乱套
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,A mess!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.84,0:05:27.89,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:27.89,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.89,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的旧房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.89,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,My old room.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.14,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是原状
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.14,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like I left it!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.10,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面可能会有线索
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.10,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's clues in here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.48,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,能帮我们找到大家的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.48,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,about where everyone went!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.31,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以来扮演侦探了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.31,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We get to play detective!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.31,0:05:43.15,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了  再小的线索也不能放过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:43.15,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, no clue is too small!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.66,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这颗花生是线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.66,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this peanut a clue?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.41,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  海绵侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.41,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good work, Detective SquarePants.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.41,0:05:55.20,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:55.20,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.92,0:05:58.75,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是线索
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:58.75,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a clue
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.09,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,再找到线索就跟我说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.09,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,but let me know if you find more.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.84,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这片隐形眼镜是线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.84,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this contact lens a clue?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.26,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.26,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, that's mine.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.26,0:06:09.97,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不小心掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:09.97,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just fell out.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.06,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.06,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.10,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.10,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.83,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我退后  你这怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.83,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stand back, you monster!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.79,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝会空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.79,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob knows karate
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.79,0:06:37.41,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我敢让他来对你耍几招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:37.41,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm not afraid to make him use it!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.04,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想跟你们打架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.04,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fight you.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.34,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要你们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.34,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need your help!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.96,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,鱿鱼妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.96,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidina!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.17,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.17,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.80,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到处都在找你跟你家人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.80,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been looking everywhere for you and your family!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you won't find them here.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.39,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切都要从派大星的时旅柜说起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.39,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It all started with Patrick's Time Closet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.39,0:06:55.89,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,事情就发生在几周前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:55.89,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,a few weeks ago...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.64,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星应该不介意我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.64,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick won't mind if I store
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,往里面存点多出来的清洁用品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,some of my extra cleaning supplies in here!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.40,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.40,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Emergency!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.74,0:07:12.07,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这巨型披萨饺凉了  得马上加热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:12.07,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,This cold jumbo calzone needs re-heating, stat!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.37,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.37,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.20,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星的超大微波柜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.20,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's walk-in microwave!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.80,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,马桶坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.80,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,The toilet's on the fritz
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.63,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才刚喝完梅干玛奇朵咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.63,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I already had my prune macchiato!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.88,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点都憋不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.88,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hold it any longer!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.13,0:07:31.76,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:31.76,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.89,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星的超大微波柜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.89,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's walk-in microwave!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.76,0:07:39.23,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得在里面方便个六小时  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:39.23,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm gonna need about six hours of privacy, so--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.24,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,它就这样把他们给抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.24,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it grabbed 'em like this!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.95,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样把他们咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.95,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it chomped 'em like that!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.83,0:08:00.71,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:00.71,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.21,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个办法  可以阻止时旅柜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.21,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a plan to stop the Time Closet!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.54,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就只要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.54,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.45,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,它居然把鱿鱼妹给吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.45,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it ate Squidina!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.78,0:08:37.28,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才刚要想起来自己有妹妹的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:37.28,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just starting to remember I had a sister!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.87,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,她没了  就只能靠我们自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.87,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,With her gone, it's up to us.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.87,0:08:43.08,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,得确保时旅柜不会再抓走别人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.58,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to make sure the Time Closet
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.08,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,doesn't get anyone else!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.71,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,门你们自己用  你们你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.71,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You keep that door to yourself, you-you-you--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.14,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.14,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Starting now!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.81,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们抓的是柜子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.81,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're hunting a closet.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.68,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,柜子有门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.68,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Closets have doors.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.69,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实柜子差不多就是门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.69,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, closets are mostly door!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.90,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1374,905)}柜子=门
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.73,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你算得对  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.73,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your math checks out, partner!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.19,0:09:15.03,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,要抓住门  就得跟门一样思考
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:15.03,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,To catch a door, we have to think like doors!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.32,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是怎么思考呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.32,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.16,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,两位朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.16,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, fellas!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.58,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你们解决难题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.58,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can help you out of this jam!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.75,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.75,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a door!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.87,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,达奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.87,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dutch!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.04,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你原来是门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.04,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a door?!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.33,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一直都是  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.33,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always have been, Patrick!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.33,0:09:31.50,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以把必备的知识通通教给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:31.50,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I can teach you everything you need to know.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.50,0:09:39.14,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要打开头脑中的感知之门就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.84,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just have to open
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:39.14,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,the doors of perception in your minds!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.56,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉有点嬉皮士的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.56,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds kind of hippie-dippie.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.23,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,没试过就别乱说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.23,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't knock it till you've tried it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.23,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,926)}敲
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.23,0:09:52.02,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,跨越知识的门槛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:52.02,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step over the threshold of knowledge!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.74,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,它只取决于一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.74,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It all hinges on one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.74,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(878,925)}铰 链
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.45,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,解锁出潜力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.45,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unlocking the potential of--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.25,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.25,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.46,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.46,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.54,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,门都喜欢双关笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.54,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,All doors love puns!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.34,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可以讲个特别烂的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.34,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can use one of those lame jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.21,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,智斗时旅柜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.21,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,to outwit the Time Closet!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.71,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.71,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.17,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没听懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.17,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, Patrick.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.47,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,门在什么时候不是门呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.47,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,When is a door not a door?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.31,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,虚掩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.31,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,When it's a jar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.31,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(880,925)}变罐子
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.66,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢各位捧场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.66,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, folks.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.12,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们整晚都在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.12,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here all night!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.38,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.38,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.38,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.38,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good as new!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.88,0:10:57.92,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:57.92,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.76,0:11:04.18,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家人取代了我过去的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:04.18,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your family took my place in the past!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.97,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要来穿越时空拯救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.97,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we go back in time and rescue 'em.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.56,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一站  去石头滩救鱿鱼妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.56,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,First stop: Squidina in Rock Bottom!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.48,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好  会去救的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.48,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure, we could do that.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.11,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就先来看电视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.11,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or we could watch some TV!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.11,0:11:19.20,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚逃跑了老半天的  确实累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.69,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I am pretty tired
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.20,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,from all that fleeing we did earlier.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.82,0:11:20.65,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:20.65,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the heck!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.03,0:11:27.08,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,先看鱿鱼妹怎么了  再去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:25.74,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll watch what happened to Squidina
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.08,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then rescue her!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.37,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,电视派对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.37,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,TV party!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.00,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能来点爆米花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.00,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have some popcorn?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.34,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还要追我的剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.34,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm watching my stories!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.01,0:11:41.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们应该是搭错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:41.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we're on the wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,车了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bus
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.31,0:11:55.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是司机  我们得回裤头村去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:55.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, sir, we need to get back to Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是什么时空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鱿鱼妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidina?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  几年后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, a few years from now--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是先离开这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just get outta here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are here?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石头滩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rock Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fn@Adobe 黑体 Std R\pos(1144,620)}石头滩
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想待在这  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna be here, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.60,0:12:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna go home
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个先在这等着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, you two wait here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边有个公交总站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a bus station over there
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去拿公交时刻表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I'm gonna go get a schedule
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place is so creepy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又好有电影感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so cinematic
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鱿鱼妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidina
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The bus is here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鱿鱼妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidina
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.71,0:12:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:12:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就搭去裤头村的下一趟车好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll grab the next bus to Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后再回到时旅柜里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and get back to the Time Closet
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺便拍点补充镜头素材
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And grab some B-roll
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.18,注释,,0,0,0,,[ B-roll：辅助主镜头的补充素材，如环境 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(870,566)}公较总占
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:14.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(920,194)}问讯处
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.14,0:13:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪模怪样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looking bizarre
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:29.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1536,346)}则所
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可名状
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Uncanny
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Teenage ne'er-do-wells
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,公交
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The bus
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1610,308)}公较
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,公交
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The bus
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.05,0:13:45.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下可好  又错过了一趟车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:45.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh great, I missed another one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想惹麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want any trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在等公交
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,waiting for the bus
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.89,0:13:53.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一听就
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:53.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,boring
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.02,0:14:00.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老古板才坐公交
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:00.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buses are for squares
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.11,0:14:03.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来搭咱便车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:03.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come take a ride with us
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我石头滩语有点生疏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My Rock Bottomese is a little rusty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一趟公交
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The next bus isn't for
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好几小时不来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hours
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞点恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pull some pranks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超级
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll be
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fun
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉这素材不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It could be great footage
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正未来迟早都会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The future will always be there
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会儿再回去也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can get back to it later
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我加入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm in
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.69,0:14:41.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:41.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我名字叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.78,0:14:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是迈克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's Mike
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是鱿鱼妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Squidina
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:20.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1476,272)}电话
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.69,0:15:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.82,0:15:27.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有话快说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:27.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it quick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.61,0:15:28.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:28.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to order
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.45,0:15:32.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三百份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:32.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,300 Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不加蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold the Krabby
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不加堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早跟你们几个小屁孩说过别再打来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you kids to stop calling here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以续杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I get a refill?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这招真是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one's
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a classic
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.81,0:16:05.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:05.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.98,0:16:06.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:06.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是我见过最酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the coolest kids I've ever
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.16,0:16:20.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷小子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:20.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,met
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aw, shucks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想在这多待几天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna hang here for days
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过一阵子再回裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom can wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so can
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the future
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.92,0:16:32.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:32.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们整到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys got me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.79,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的  拍到的素材都丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.79,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aw, man, I lost my footage.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.79,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  鱿鱼妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.79,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidina.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.21,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过呢  我们修好了时旅柜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.21,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,But hey, we fixed the Time Closet!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.30,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.30,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且你看  我宝贵的回忆也修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And look, we fixed my precious memory.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.18,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  来找找你其他家人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.18,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's find the rest of your family.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.40,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找到老爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.40,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found Dad!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.06,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸  你怎么会变得这么小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.06,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad, why are you so small?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.40,0:17:32.40,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  把他救回来就会变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:32.40,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, he'll be bigger when we bring him back.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.41,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,是酷乐湖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.41,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's Goo Lagoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:39.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1268,692)}欢迎来到酷乐湖
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.29,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,去救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.29,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go get him!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.04,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.04,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.79,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,先看看才更好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.79,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's more fun to watch first!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  有在附近看到个巨型披萨饺没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, pal, have you seen a jumbo calzone around here?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我继续去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, back to the hunt
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能借几个这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I borrow a couple of these?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我儿子的小伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, that was my son's little friend
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道他有没有看到我的披萨饺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's seen my calzone
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  再加上两个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, with the addition of two
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.20,0:18:29.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,数一下  两个棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:29.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,count 'em, two marshmallows
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heya, sonny
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有看到个超大披萨饺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a big calzone?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  星爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Star
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在在给大家好好表现一下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of in the middle of impressing everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,举重是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pumping iron, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒是可以给你指点几下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I could give you a few pointers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽量张开脚踝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep your ankles as wide as possible
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双膝并拢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knees locked together
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我比较喜欢双手交叉的握法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cross grip is my preferred method
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脊背弯曲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back nice and rounded
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,头抬高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Head high
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.07,0:18:58.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:58.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tongue out
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼻孔张开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nostrils flared
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后开唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And sing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's alright
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我给你做下正确示范
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me show you how it's done
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,仔细看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now watch closely
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这招叫做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is what they call
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.17,0:19:19.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸神力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"dad strength"
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,星爸  真是太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Star, that was hilarious
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.12,0:19:49.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你原来这么搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:49.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you were so funny
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里喜欢破裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry likes ripped pants
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样的话  我再给一条慈父忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In that case, here's another fatherly tip
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.80,0:19:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要多带一条裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always carry an extra pair of pants
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是别人这么搞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If it was anybody else
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.10,0:20:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没多久这笑话就腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that joke would grow stale and tiresome before long
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.94,0:20:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我可以整天看你破裤子  这位老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I could watch you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rip your pants all day long, dad-dude
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为星爸欢呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it for Mr. Star
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,228)}喜剧王
