Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.77,0:21:01.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,塞西尔先生  模特都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:01.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Cecil, the models are ready
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就开破吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let 'em rip
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,塞西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cecil
