Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.17,0:21:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,破了几千条裤子后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,236)}破裤子公司
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.51,0:21:31.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不到破裤子能破出这么个时尚大业
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who knew ripping my pants
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would lead to a fashion empire?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.64,0:21:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,塞西尔先生  外面有一大群人想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Cecil, there's a large group of people outside for you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.27,0:21:38.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定都是我的死忠粉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:38.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those must be my adoring fans
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.40,0:21:39.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:39.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Linda
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家圣诞快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Season's greetings, everyo--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛打我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.53,0:21:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你骗我们大冬天把衣服全撕破了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,F-For convincing us to rip all our clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:56.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(474,158)}我们冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the m-middle of winter
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.12,0:21:56.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都冷冷冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:56.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we're all f-f-f-freezing
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.26,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在能把他救回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.26,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now can we pull him out of there?!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.09,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好戏正要上场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.09,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's getting to the good part!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.09,0:22:07.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家别激动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:07.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, now, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.88,0:22:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该有你们想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I get what you all want
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终极大撕破
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the ultimate rip
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.35,0:22:17.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:17.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.86,0:22:25.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:25.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.44,0:22:26.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好不好看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:26.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get him
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.28,0:22:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两半一起抓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Both of him
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:41.63,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}未完待续
